        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="195" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>When you depreciate a fixed asset by using the equally divided depreciation method, the depreciation amount is equally divided among the fiscal periods within the useful life of the fixed asset.</source>
        </trans-unit>
